<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  title="CV | Dr. Haitham Abdelmonem El-Ghareeb"
  description="Curriculum vitae of Dr. Haitham Abdelmonem El-Ghareeb, Associate Professor of Information Systems at Mansoura University."
>
  <main class="page-main">
    <section class="shell hero hero--detail">
      <p class="hero__eyebrow">Curriculum Vitae</p>
      <h1 class="hero__title">Dr. Haitham Abdelmonem El-Ghareeb</h1>
      <p class="hero__lead">
        Associate Professor of Information Systems, Faculty of Computers and Information,
        Mansoura University, Egypt. This page brings together personal, academic, and
        professional information based on the supplied biography and the attached academic CV.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="shell section">
      <div class="grid-two">
        <article class="content-card">
          <p class="content-card__meta">Personal Information</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Core Profile</h2>
          <ul class="list-clean">
            <li>Name: Haitham Abdelmonem El-Ghareeb.</li>
            <li>Current position: Associate Professor of Information Systems, Faculty of Computers and Information, Mansoura University, Egypt.</li>
            <li>Place of birth: Kuwait.</li>
            <li>Nationality and place of residence: Egypt.</li>
            <li>Date of birth: 03 September 1981, corresponding to 5 Dhu al-Qi'dah 1401 AH.</li>
            <li>Marital status: Married with dependents.</li>
            <li>School of jurisprudence: Hanbali.</li>
          </ul>
