            <li>University email: helghareeb@mans.edu.eg</li>
            <li>Mobile: 00201222330847</li>
            <li>Google Scholar: https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=f66uaewAAAAJ&hl=en</li>
            <li>LinkedIn: https://eg.linkedin.com/in/helghareeb</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="shell section">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="section-kicker">Academic Record</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Degrees and Appointments</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-two">
        <article class="feature-card">
          <h3>Academic degrees</h3>
          <ul class="list-clean">
            <li>B.Sc. in Information Systems, Mansoura University, 2004.</li>
            <li>M.Sc. in Information Systems, Mansoura University, 2008.</li>
            <li>Ph.D. in Information Systems, Mansoura University, 2011.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card">
          <h3>Academic progression</h3>
          <ul class="list-clean">
            <li>Teaching Assistant, Information Systems Department, Mansoura University, 2005.</li>
            <li>Assistant Lecturer, Information Systems Department, Mansoura University, 2008.</li>
            <li>Lecturer, Information Systems Department, Mansoura University, 2012.</li>
            <li>Associate Professor, Information Systems Department, Mansoura University, since 2019.</li>
            <li>External assignment: Associate Professor of Information Systems, Computer Science Department, Zulfi University, Saudi Arabia, 2015 to 2017.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="shell section">
      <div class="grid-two">
        <article class="content-card">
          <p class="content-card__meta">Recognition</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Selected distinctions</h2>
          <ul class="list-clean">
            <li>EMC Featured Proven Professional, December 2015.</li>
            <li>Huawei ICT Competition 2019-2020 Global Final Grand Prize, Cloud Track.</li>
            <li>Academic and research activity in information systems, enterprise integration, e-learning, and intelligent systems.</li>
