            <li>Enterprise architecture, enterprise integration, and SOA.</li>
            <li>E-learning and distributed integrated systems.</li>
            <li>Artificial intelligence, machine learning, and cloud computing.</li>
            <li>Applying modern technical means in the service of Islamic scholarship and manuscript studies.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
