        students of knowledge, and people of virtue, and prays that God bless this ummah, restore
        its honor, accept sincere efforts, and employ them in what pleases Him.
      </p>
      <p>Abu Malik Haitham bin Abdelmonem El-Ghareeb<br />Mansoura, Egypt</p>
